snippet.title: Terraria: The Stars Above | 1.0 RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
'Conquer the world's evils, Starfarers at your side.'
https://discord.gg/starsabove | Join the Discord today!


With over 700k downloads, the Stars Above finally reaches version 1.0.
Read more on the Terraria Fourm: https://forums.terraria.org/index.php?threads/the-stars-above-mod-conquer-the-worlds-evils-starfarers-at-your-side.105442/
